        Create a archive.values handler given an event stream. If all goes well, processing should stop after each event (and hence should stop after the first event).
        Parameters:
        pvName - The name of PV
        is - InputStream
        source -  
        expectedDBRType - This is the expected DBR type. This can be null in which case we do a best guess.
